{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSURL","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL to process.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test device registration"}]},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Deep link tracking","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app."}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"handleOpenURL:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pw